section.t:
For collective remove notifications,
         if CLASS is not 255 (ANY) and TYPE is not 255 (ANY)
         then for the given name this deletes all records of the specified type in the specified class.

For collective remove notifications,
         if CLASS is not 255 (ANY) and TYPE is 255 (ANY)
         then for the given name this deletes all records of all types in the specified class.

